dct_title_s: Kevin Healey's travel map of Galapagos Islands.
dct_description_sm: Includes text, indexed ancillary map of "Charles Darwin Station," 2 other ancillary maps, location map, publisher's index map, and color illustrations. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Depths shown by isolines. Panel title. On panel title: 340. Photographs by Marylee Stephenson on panel. Credits: Compilation and cartography by Kevin Healey; drawings and text by Hilary Bradt; revised cartography by David Sami.
